1. On je izuzetno uspešan *vrlo* brzo. (He is extremely successful very quickly.)
2. Njegov uspeh je *vrlo* impresivan. (His success is very impressive.)
3. Ona je *vrlo* obrazovana. (She is very educated.)
4. Njegov glas je *vrlo* glasan. (His voice is very loud.)
5. Ona je *vrlo* lepa. (She is very beautiful.)
6. Ona je *vrlo* dobra u matematici. (She is very good in mathematics.)
7. Ona je *vrlo* uspešna. (She is very successful.)
8. On je *vrlo* inteligentan. (He is very intelligent.)
9. Ona je *vrlo* pažljiva. (She is very careful.)
10. On je *vrlo* uspešan. (He is very successful.)